---
title: Spinach, Mushroom and Bacon Puff with Seared Tomatoes
description: This fun twist on a pizza is made with puff pastry instead of pizza dough. A flaky crust topped with a delicious creamy Canadian peameal bacon, mushrooms and spinach? Yes, please!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spinach-mushroom-and-bacon-puff-3ff95aa8.jpg
